  "description": "Represents a single log entry with all relevant contextual information.\nThis interface defines the contract for log data passed through the logging system.",
  "title": "Interface ILogEntry",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry' data-commentId='T:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry'>Interface ILogEntry    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L39'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h1>\r\n <div class=\"facts text-secondary\">\r\n<dl><dt>Namespace</dt><dd><a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.html'>Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions</a></dd></dl><dl><dt>Assembly</dt><dd>Alis.dll</dd></dl>\r\n</div><p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Represents a single log entry with all relevant contextual information.\nThis interface defines the contract for log data passed through the logging system.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public interface ILogEntry</code></pre><h2 class='section'>Properties</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.CorrelationId' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.CorrelationId' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry_CorrelationId'>CorrelationId    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L74'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the correlation ID for tracing related log entries.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>string CorrelationId { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Exception' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Exception' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry_Exception'>Exception    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L64'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the exception associated with this entry, if any.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>Exception Exception { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.exception'>Exception</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Level' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Level' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry_Level'>Level    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L44'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the log level indicating severity of this entry.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>LogLevel Level { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.LogLevel.html'>LogLevel</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.LoggerName' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.LoggerName' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry_LoggerName'>LoggerName    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L59'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the name/category of the logger that created this entry.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>string LoggerName { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Message' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Message' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry_Message'>Message    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L49'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the primary message of the log entry.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>string Message { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Properties' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Properties' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry_Properties'>Properties    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L79'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the structured data (key-value pairs) associated with this entry.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>IReadOnlyDictionary&lt;string, object&gt; Properties { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.generic.ireadonlydictionary-2'>IReadOnlyDictionary</a>&lt;<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.string'>string</a>, <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Scopes' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Scopes' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry_Scopes'>Scopes    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L84'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the scope/context information for this log entry.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>IReadOnlyList&lt;object&gt; Scopes { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.collections.generic.ireadonlylist-1'>IReadOnlyList</a>&lt;<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object'>object</a>&gt;  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.ThreadId' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.ThreadId' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry_ThreadId'>ThreadId    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L69'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the thread ID where the log entry was created.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>int ThreadId { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int32'>int</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Timestamp' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.Timestamp' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Abstractions_ILogEntry_Timestamp'>Timestamp    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/6_Ideation/Logging/src/Abstractions/ILogEntry.cs#L54'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Abstractions.ILogEntry.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets the timestamp when the log entry was created.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>DateTime Timestamp { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.datetime'>DateTime</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
